cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU to '10.0.0.1', an unreachable IP address, causing CU to fail in connecting to the UPF due to routing misconfiguration.

du.explanation_en: Setting local_s_address to '999.999.999.999', which is an invalid IP address format, causing SCTP binding failures.
du.explanation_zh: 将 local_s_address 设置为 '999.999.999.999'，这是无效的 IP 地址格式，导致 SCTP 绑定失败。
